{"tid":2349314,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Viu到完場勿劇透] 2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮（6）","createTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T12:49:43.000Z","uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17c901e58fd5e0aa03d5a2ab3c803f32bb0a46a8","tid":2349314,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮，是由香港商業電台舉辦的一個本地音樂頒獎典禮，將於2021年1月1日晚上7時於九龍灣國際展貿中心舉行，本屆頒獎禮雖恢復為實體形式，但將不設現場觀眾，以保持2019冠狀病毒病疫情期間的社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJ3LGbj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJ3LGbj.png&h=57b2cc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本屆主題定為「一切從音樂再開始」，美術主題為一輛叱咤火炬形狀的飛船在火星中準備起飛，帶領大家再次踏上奇妙的音樂之旅， 寓意誠邀大家一同登上飛船、重新向未知的將來出發。<br />\n<br />\n直播及轉播：<br />\n叱咤903&mdash;聲音直播<br />\n<a href=\"http://my903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=06f8dde6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://my903.com</a>、<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=49ccdd37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://881903.com</a>&mdash;網上串流視像直播<br />\n手機程式 Hong Kong Toolbar（Android 用戶）、商台節目重溫 app / Hong Kong Toolbar（iOS用戶）&mdash;影片直播<br />\nViuTV&mdash;影片轉播<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">此post為ViuTV區，網上live post請移玉步</span><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><ins>劇透撚仆街死啦</ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e8d68f18f97effe8f96efd98f8b7b7ce75a56646","tid":2349314,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依d擺到明知有獎先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>冇獎佢鬼會黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj